Requirements
============

glibmm		2.4.0 http://www.gtkmm.org/
libxml++	2.6.0 http://libxmlplusplus.sourceforge.net/
libtool		1.5
automake	1.4
autoconf	2.50

Installation
============

See documentation available on VLE wesite http://vle.univ-littoral.fr

The fallowing commands compile et install VLE:

$ ./autogen.sh

or

$ autoreconf --force --install
$ ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
$ make
$ make install
